title: #208: Pad Thai (@GeoffKeith)
itunes:title: Pad Thai with Geoff Keith
description: Geoff Keith met me at the Comedy Store to talk about all his amazing trips to Southeast Asia. He's been there a few times. To the Phillipines, to Thailand, and somewhere else that I'm forgetting. There's some pretty cool adventures in there and it really makes me want to go see those places for myself.
